dcterms:description: The FH-V1 dataset contains 4,964 image samples from 247 unique subjects, captured during two sessions, showcasing various facial expressions and eyebrow movements to reveal forehead wrinkles. It is designed to ensure temporal stability and was collected remotely using a mobile application in a natural setting.
dcterms:title: Forehead Creases version 1 (FH-V1)
